      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "EKS health for a single Data Platform account, from CloudWatch **Container Insights**. Choose an **Account** and a **Cluster** at the top. Panels use CloudWatch Metrics Insights, so they aggregate across nodes/pods without naming them. The cluster, node and pod panels need Container Insights enabled on the cluster; the load-balancer panels at the bottom cover all Application Load Balancers in the account."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Cluster",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "panels": []
